name: Giga City Streets #4
description: Jade Martinez - Born and raised in the gritty alleys of a corporate-controlled dystopia, Jade Martinez emerged as a fierce anti-corporate fighter. His early years were a brutal battle for survival, and the scars of poverty and inequality were etched deep into his soul. Jade's transformation into an uncompromising guerrilla leader was born from a searing desire to dismantle the oppressive regime that had perpetuated the divide between the privileged elite and the destitute masses.
